- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning models for text data.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper focuses on developing machine learning models for predicting ICD-10 codes.
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is a possible category as the paper discusses the potential impact of automated ICD coding on healthcare and society.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with developing AI models for automated ICD coding.
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possible category as the paper involves extracting key evidence to make predictions more convincing and explainable.
